31#include "mech_locl.h"
32
33GSSAPI_LIB_FUNCTION OM_uint32 GSSAPI_LIB_CALL
34gss_inquire_cred_by_mech(OM_uint32 *minor_status,
35 gss_const_cred_id_t cred_handle,
36 const gss_OID mech_type,
37 gss_name_t *cred_name,
38 OM_uint32 *initiator_lifetime,
39 OM_uint32 *acceptor_lifetime,
40 gss_cred_usage_t *cred_usage)
41{
42 OM_uint32 major_status;
43 gssapi_mech_interface m;
44 struct _gss_mechanism_cred *mcp;
45 gss_cred_id_t mc;
46 gss_name_t mn;
47 struct _gss_name *name;
48
49 *minor_status = 0;
50 if (cred_name)
51 *cred_name = GSS_C_NO_NAME;
52 if (initiator_lifetime)
53 *initiator_lifetime = 0;
54 if (acceptor_lifetime)
55 *acceptor_lifetime = 0;
56 if (cred_usage)
57 *cred_usage = 0;
58
59 m = __gss_get_mechanism(mech_type);
60 if (!m)
61 return (GSS_S_NO_CRED);
62
63 if (cred_handle != GSS_C_NO_CREDENTIAL) {
64 struct _gss_cred *cred = (struct _gss_cred *) cred_handle;
65 HEIM_SLIST_FOREACH(mcp, &cred->gc_mc, gmc_link)
66 if (mcp->gmc_mech == m)
67 break;
68 if (!mcp)
69 return (GSS_S_NO_CRED);
70 mc = mcp->gmc_cred;
71 } else {
72 mc = GSS_C_NO_CREDENTIAL;
73 }
74
75 major_status = m->gm_inquire_cred_by_mech(minor_status, mc, mech_type,
76 &mn, initiator_lifetime, acceptor_lifetime, cred_usage);
77 if (major_status != GSS_S_COMPLETE) {
78 _gss_mg_error(m, major_status, *minor_status);
79 return (major_status);
80 }
81
82 if (cred_name) {
83 name = _gss_make_name(m, mn);
84 if (!name) {
85 m->gm_release_name(minor_status, &mn);
86 return (GSS_S_NO_CRED);
87 }
88 *cred_name = (gss_name_t) name;
89 } else
90 m->gm_release_name(minor_status, &mn);
91
92
93 return (GSS_S_COMPLETE);
94}
